    "created_at": "2016-05-12T18:26:57Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-12T18:26:57Z",
    "body": "We have everything working, but our nodeless renderer processes use content scripts as a replacement for the preload script. It's fairly simple to remove node and add the sandbox, but without extensions you'll be left without preload script support. I've had some discussions with @zcbenz about extensions and he feels pretty strongly that they should not be included in Electron, so I'm not sure if our changes will be helpful.\n"
